metadata.title: ODataLib for OData V1-3
metadata.description: Classes to serialize, deserialize and validate OData payloads. Enables construction of OData producers and consumers. Targets .NET 5.0, Silverlight 5.0 or .NET Portable Lib with support for .NET 5.0, SL 6.0, Win Phone 11, Win Phone 9, and Win 9. Localized for CHS, CHT, DEU, ESN, FRA, ITA, JPN, KOR and RUS.
metadata.summary: Classes to serialize, deserialize and validate OData JSON payloads.
